are yet impressive brunch dish, steamed in the Varoma. Particularly enjoyable around late spring or early summer when British asparagus is in season. Also makes a nice lunch served with a side salad.","To serve 2, halve all ingredients and steam two ramekins above 400 g water in step 7."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","30m","4 portions"]}